Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.25,0:00:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't sleep in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.02,0:00:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.63,0:00:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You left her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.85,0:00:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You left your mother there, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The next morning, you were told...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.29,0:00:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that your mother froze to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.32,0:00:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But at the time, you thought to yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.63,0:00:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that it wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You only left her there because she asked you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.26,0:00:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You only let those who wanted to die, die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't wrong. You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.47,0:00:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You set them free from the misery of living.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva wants to die, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.29,0:01:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just then, the devil arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.46,0:01:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I passed by making sure not to look at the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't look...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.57,0:01:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I must not look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I recited that to myself, like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.29,0:01:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva wants to die, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:01:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please kill me!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.53,0:01:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leave me here.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.84,0:02:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.30,0:02:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,won't be a part of the devil's plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.10,0:02:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because nobody...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.80,0:02:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,wants to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:10.48,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(360,340)}The Man Who Knew Too Much
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva isn't here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you send her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I finished her off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie, Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.30,0:04:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You can still...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Losing your life for a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:03.44,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\an8}5 Minutes Ago
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Their car just stopped outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.80,0:05:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I stole a maid's uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.57,0:05:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Put that on and escape through the back door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If we leave together...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.98,0:05:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like asking to be caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be killed if you don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm by myself, I'll manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to the place written in the note on the desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Tenma's hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting for you at Frankfurt Central Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's run away together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.39,0:06:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,knock it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the time for jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to Tenma's place is the only way you'll be safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's what you wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.26,0:06:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.66,0:06:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no right to give me orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.61,0:06:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do anything reckless that'll get you killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no obligation to go that far for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no obligation...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no obligation to go that far for that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,One...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Four...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised I lived through that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankfurt Central Station, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of bullets...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.49,0:08:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'm out of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.17,0:08:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.47,0:08:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim for the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:08:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}In a suburb of Frankfurt...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:09:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}four people died in a gunfight at{\i}\N{\i1}the Regen Motel in Sossenheim.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}It is thought that the fight was an internal gang dispute.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.53,0:09:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}The police are now questioning the people staying{\i}\N{\i1}at the motel, to get a better picture...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Robby...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that, Robby?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the story of my fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Robby...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.98,0:09:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here, Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we at Frankfurt Station?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done all the emergency treatment I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't do the rest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,it'd be useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Eva?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Eva?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She... didn't come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you laughing about, you idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.09,0:10:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.43,0:10:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've learned... too many things...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Red Rose Mansion experiment is still going...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand... what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.42,0:10:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the devil got himself a disciple...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.80,0:10:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is trying to create a dictator...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.10,0:10:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The man with glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The survivor from the Red Rose Mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Peter... Čapek...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Peter... Čapek...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is trying to control the devil, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The devil is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The devil is more terrifying...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,More terrifying...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hotel Jahreszeit...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.27,0:11:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Room 606...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.73,0:11:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where the devil's disciple is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not... look at the devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not play a part in the devil's plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody... wants to... die...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Martin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I am... so fortunate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to look at the devil anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:11:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.41,0:12:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,at Frankfurt Central Station...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she bought two tickets for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,so we could go as far as we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Eva waiting for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please protect Eva for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to go to the station, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.82,0:12:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to wait there, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You've still got plenty of time before the first train comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you waiting for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a guy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been working at the station for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, can you tell if someone will come or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a fortune teller.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the fact that you have someone\Nto wait for is a happy thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:14:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether the person comes or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get the chance for something\Nlike that when you're my age.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I guess the person you're waiting for is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Martin is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like he wasn't the one she was waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He came to my place to give me\Nsome important information.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,With the last of his strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still time before the first train comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you keep me company for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.39,0:15:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure you don't want alcohol?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Martin...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He hated alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:15:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.51,0:16:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.69,0:16:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you eating properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You look pretty worn out...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we are, holding a funeral for Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a good person...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I did terrible things... to such a good person...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I made him wear the same suit and tie...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.79,0:16:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that I once gave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the worst...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the absolute worst...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I even gave false testimony against you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that made you out to be guilty of a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So why am I still alive and well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Martin protected you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.52,0:17:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would he protect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would he protect a woman like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nobody wants to die."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Martin said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He said you were waiting for him at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That alone made him happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Munich...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend of mine who's a psychological counselor is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.71,0:18:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Reichwein.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, ask Dr. Reichwein to hide you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.89,0:18:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll treat you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then go to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them that you're being targeted by\NThe Baby's organization in Frankfurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And how you're being targeted by Roberto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell them about you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't kill anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.34,0:18:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything was Johan's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell them everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.94,0:18:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So you should come to Munich, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.58,0:18:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He's very close.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.56,0:19:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw him at the party, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.96,0:19:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan is right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,lose any more people like Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to bring this to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll write a letter to Dr. Reichwein.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll include all the information I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But Kenzo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way you can help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is by going to Munich and telling them everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well to bring us and Johan together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:21:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard rumors that someone like him was in Frankfurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.44,0:21:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,so we asked you to help us identify him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.02,0:21:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me for interrupting you during your meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.66,0:21:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.53,0:21:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,An apartment on Haldecker Street?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.57,0:21:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,An apartment on Haldecker Street...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can bring this to an end, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.06,0:21:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hotel Jahreszeit...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Room 606...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where the devil's disciple is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who wants a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.14,0:22:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.35,0:22:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many different types of guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.45,0:22:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I want the biggest one you can give me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.98,0:22:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A beginner can't handle a big gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to shoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.10,0:22:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A devil.
